description:
➤ Amazing Facts Media Library - https://www.amazingfacts.org/media-library
➤ Tune into AF Radio - https://www.amazingfacts.org/media-library/listen

Long before Pastor Doug Batchelor crossed the Pacific to the Philippines from Sacramento, the Philippines Amazing Facts Center of Evangelism—or PAFCOE—team has been training Bible students in the art of outreach. 46 new students are being trained to give Bible studies and to reach their communities for Christ with love, compassion, and healing. Pastor Doug was recently able to spend time with these eager students, encouraging them in their dreams to become better witnesses for Jesus Christ.

Pastor Doug also took time to speak to the inmates at the largest Women’s Correctional Institute, offering them precious words of hope from God’s Word. They felt blessed that Amazing Facts would come to them in person and learned about the eternal freedom found only in Jesus Christ. Many hearts were touched for the Lord…
